## 0. Gap Analysis (What's Real vs. False Positives)

Cross-referenced both plans against `super-council.py` to eliminate false positives.

### Already Implemented (No Work Needed)

| Finding | Source | Reality | Evidence |
|---------|--------|---------|----------|
| Infinite-loop in `transition_to` (no retreat) | 6-phase P0#1 | Already retreats to SCOUT on retry exhaustion | Line 2231-2244 |
| No retreat from HUMAN_GATE to SCOUT | 6-phase P0#6 | `VALID_TRANSITIONS[HUMAN_GATE]` includes `SCOUT` | Line 2096 |
| No `PENDING_REVIEW` state | 6-phase P1#8 | Phase in `ALL_PHASES`, `VALID_TRANSITIONS`, executor wired | Lines 2076, 2095, 5053 |
| No `COHESIVENESS_REVIEW` phase | 6-phase C1 | Phase exists with co-chair delegation + static analysis fallback | Line 5099 |
| INDEX failure тЖТ DONE ambiguity | 6-phase P0#5 | Docstring states "INDEX failure тЖТ FAILED (not DONE)" | Line 2200 |
| Path-traversal in `MigrationManager` | 6-phase P0#3 | `MigrationManager` class does not exist in codebase | grep: 0 results |

### Confirmed Gaps (Real Work)

| Finding | Severity | Source | Unit |
|---------|----------|--------|------|
| Dead `PHASE_EXECUTORS` reference | HIGH | Co-chair review | Unit 1 |
| `_auto_index_file` wrong receiver | HIGH | Co-chair review | Unit 1 |
| `UnboundLocalError` in `_handle_pipeline` | HIGH | Co-chair review | Unit 1 |
| Artifacts never stored between phases | HIGH | Co-chair review | Unit 1 |
| **Duplicate pipelines from timestamp collisions** | HIGH | Structural gap | Unit 1.5 |
| **No (task, project_id) dedup lookup** | HIGH | Structural gap | Unit 1.5 |
| **`_delegate()` bypasses pipeline tracking** | HIGH | Structural gap | Unit 1.5 |
| **3 independent ID generators, no canonical ID** | HIGH | Structural gap | Unit 1.5 |
| Reviewer auto-dispatch not wired | HIGH | 6-phase P0#2 | Unit 14 |
| No diff-check before BUILD | MODERATE | 6-phase P0#4 | Unit 15 |
| Global attempt ceiling hardcoded (10) | MODERATE | 6-phase P1#9 | Unit 16 |
| Tool names not validated in `_delegate()` | MODERATE | 6-phase P1#10 | Unit 16 |
| Recall-then-validate worktree failure path | MODERATE | 6-phase P1#11 | Unit 16 |
