- **GREEN:** Implement `MicroModelEnricher`:
  - `enrich_artifact(run_id, phase, content)` тАФ generate summary, tags, keywords
  - `enrich_event_window(run_id, events)` тАФ summarize event sequences
  - `enrich_failure(run_id, error)` тАФ classify failure type
  - `should_index_full_text(content)` тАФ decide if full-text indexing is worth it
  - Create `artifact_summaries`, `event_window_summaries`, `failure_classifications` tables
  - Wire as background thread triggered on `transition_to()` commit
- **REFACTOR:** Update `ContextRouter.get_run_snapshot()` to include enrichment data. Update `MemoryLayer.ingest_artifact()` to prefer enriched summaries.
- **Verification:** `pytest tests/test_micro_model.py -v` тАФ enrichment runs async, doesn't block transitions. Fallback works when micro-model unavailable. Summaries improve recall quality.
