| Split-brain: 4 state stores | HIGH | тЬЕ Fixed | Unit 2 тАФ SQLite as canonical, remove `state_json` |
| `_delegate()` bypasses tracking | HIGH | тЬЕ Fixed | Unit 1.5 тАФ always call `_get_or_create_pipeline()` |
| 3 independent ID generators | HIGH | тЬЕ Fixed | Unit 1.5 тАФ single `uuid4().hex` generator |
| Race condition on `attempt_number` | HIGH | тЬЕ Fixed | Unit 3 тАФ `BEGIN IMMEDIATE ... COMMIT` |
| `LIKE` dedup matches substrings | MODERATE | тЬЕ Fixed | Unit 1.5 тАФ `WHERE task = ?` exact match |
| Truncated UUID (`hex[:12]`) | MODERATE | тЬЕ Fixed | Unit 1.5 тАФ full `uuid4().hex` |
| `max_global_attempts` not persisted | MODERATE | тЬЕ Fixed | Unit 11 тАФ store in `workflow_definitions` |
| `_pipeline_lock` in-process only | MODERATE | тЬЕ Fixed | Unit 1.5 тАФ `UNIQUE(task_hash, project_id)` |
| Phase registry friction | MODERATE | тЬЕ Fixed | Unit 2 тАФ auto-upsert in orchestrator init |
| Sub-delegations missing `project_id` | LOW | тЬЕ Fixed | Unit 1.5 тАФ propagate `project_id` |
| Write amplification on `event_log` | LOW | тЬЕ Fixed | Unit 2 тАФ drop unused indexes |

